{"doc":{"isMarkdown":true,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"visibility","mdn_url":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/SVG/Attribute/visibility","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)","sidebarHTML":"","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p>« <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/SVG/Attribute\">SVG 属性参考主页</a></p>\n<p><code>visibility</code>属性让你能够控制一个图形元素的可见性。用了值<code>hidden</code>或者值<code>collapse</code>，当前的图形元素将不可见。</p>\n<div class=\"notecard note\" id=\"sect1\">\n  <p><strong>备注：</strong> 如果 <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/SVG/Element/tspan\"><code>&lt;tspan&gt;</code></a>元素、<a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/SVG/Element/tref\"><code>&lt;tref&gt;</code></a>元素或<a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/SVG/Element/altGlyph\"><code>&lt;altGlyph&gt;</code></a>元素上的<code>visibility</code>属性设置为<code>hidden</code>，则文本变得不可见，但是依然占用文本布局计算的空间。</p>\n</div>\n<p>根据属性<code><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/SVG/Attribute/pointer-events\">pointer-events</a></code>的值，图形元素如果属性<code>visibility</code> 值设置为 <code>hidden</code>，依然能够响应事件。</p>\n<p>作为一个外观属性，它可以直接用作 CSS 样式表内部的属性。请阅读<a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/CSS/visibility\"><code>css visibility</code></a>以了解更多信息。</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"用法","title":"用法","isH3":false,"content":"<table>\n  <thead>\n    <tr>\n      <th>类别</th>\n      <th>外观属性</th>\n    </tr>\n  </thead>\n  <tbody>\n    <tr>\n      <td>值</td>\n      <td><strong>visible</strong> | hidden | collapse | inherit</td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <td>可变性</td>\n      <td>Yes</td>\n    </tr>\n  </tbody>\n</table>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"示例","title":"示例","isH3":false,"content":""}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"元素","title":"元素","isH3":false,"content":"<p>下列元素楞以使用<code>visibility</code>属性：</p>\n<ul>\n  <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/SVG/Element#graphics\">图形元素</a> »</li>\n  <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/SVG/Element#text_content_elements\">文本内容元素</a> »</li>\n</ul>"}},{"type":"specifications","value":{"title":"规范","id":"规范","isH3":false,"specifications":[{"bcdSpecificationURL":"https://svgwg.org/svg2-draft/render.html#VisibilityControl","title":"Scalable Vector Graphics (SVG) 1.1 (Second Edition)"}],"query":"svg.attributes.presentation.visibility"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"参见","title":"参见","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n  <li>属性<code><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/SVG/Attribute/display\">display</a></code></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/CSS/visibility\"><code>css visibility</code></a></li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"用法","id":"用法"},{"text":"示例","id":"示例"},{"text":"元素","id":"元素"},{"text":"规范","id":"规范"},{"text":"参见","id":"参见"}],"summary":"« SVG 属性参考主页","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-10-01T03:41:16.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"visibility","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"}],"source":{"folder":"zh-cn/web/svg/attribute/visibility","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/zh-cn/web/svg/attribute/visibility/index.md","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/921c46a374ab0a9f4cc809af0370f8c412e54701","filename":"index.md"},"parents":[{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web","title":"Web 开发技术"},{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/SVG","title":"SVG：可缩放矢量图形"},{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/SVG/Attribute","title":"SVG 属性参考"},{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/SVG/Attribute/visibility","title":"visibility"}],"pageTitle":"visibility - SVG：可缩放矢量图形 | MDN","noIndexing":false}}